---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contacto | FiscalPro">
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Contacta con nosotros</h1>
		<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-12 text-center">
			Resuelve tus dudas fiscales o solicita un presupuesto sin compromiso.
		</p>
		
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
			<form class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm space-y-6">
				<div>
					<label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2">Nombre</label>
					<input type="text" class="w-full border border-slate-300 p-3 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none" />
				</div>
				<div>
					<label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2">Email</label>
					<input type="email" class="w-full border border-slate-300 p-3 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none" />
				</div>
				<div>
					<label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2">Mensaje</label>
					<textarea rows="5" class="w-full border border-slate-300 p-3 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 outline-none"></textarea>
				</div>
				<button class="w-full bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-800 transition">
					Enviar Mensaje
				</button>
			</form>

			<div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-8">
				<div class="bg-green-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-green-100 text-center">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-900 mb-4">¿Prefieres WhatsApp?</h2>
					<p class="text-green-700 mb-6">Atención inmediata para tus consultas fiscales.</p>
					<a href="https://wa.me/34697368100" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-green-700 transition shadow-lg">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 1 1-7.6-10.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8.9L22 4Z"/></svg>
						Chat Directo: 697368100
					</a>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100">
					<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">Ubicación Central</h2>
					<p class="text-blue-700">Valencia, España</p>
					<p class="text-sm text-blue-600 mt-2">Disponibilidad para reuniones presenciales y online.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
